body: Ok so you know how in Doctor Who the word “doctor” has different meanings depending on the language and the people? What if they do that with the word “Captain” and so Carol starts going by Captain Marvel bc of the space adventures she has and the reputation she has created. summary: Tracking for Shazam's Opening Weekend Jumps to $50 Million
title: Tracking for Shazam's Opening Weekend Jumps to $50 Million
body:
Tracking for Shazam’s Opening Weekend Jumps to $50 Million

With only a few weeks before its debut, Shazam! may be sitting in the wake of Marvel’s Captain Marvel, but the original Captain Marvel still looks like it will have a big opening weekend.

Reports just weeks ago were tracking its opening weekend at $40 million, but positive word-of-mouth has already jumped that number up to $50 million.

After Captain Marvel’s$153 million that might not seem like a…
